						<h3 class="contactDetailsSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--contactDetails">Have a project in mind?</h3>

						<p class="contactDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--contactIntro">
							Got a question, idea, or project you'd like to discuss? I'd love to hear from you. Whether you're looking for a new website, a redesign, ongoing support, or simply need some advice, feel free
							to get in touch.
						</p>

						<p class="contactDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--contactIntro">Meetings are by appointment and can be arranged at a time that works best for both of us.</p>
