			<section class="contactPage__availabilityDetailsSection availabilityDetailsSection contactPageSection">
				<div id="businesshours" class="linkDiv"></div>
				<div class="contactDetailsSection__sectionHeading sectionHeading">
					<h2 class="contactDetailsSection__headingH2 sectionHeading__headingH2 headingH2 headingH2--availability">Business Hours</h2>
					<hr class="contactDetailsSection__hr sectionHeading__hr hr hr--availability" />
					<p class="contactDetailsSection__headingH2Tagline sectionHeading__headingH2Tagline headingH2Tagline headingH2Tagline--availability">available right now</p>
				</div>

				<div class="contactPageSection__contactPageSectionContentContainer availabilityDetailsSection__availabilityDetailsContentContainer">
					<div class="availabilityDetailsSection__availabilityDetailsTextContainer">
						<h3 class="availabilityDetailsSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--availabilityDetails">When am I available?</h3>

						<p class="availabilityDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--availabilityIntro">
							I’m available online during the hours below. This is when I’m actively working, handling projects, and typically able to respond to messages and new enquiries.
						</p>

						<p class="availabilityDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--availabilityIntro">Outside of these times, responses may be delayed, but I’ll get back to you as soon as I’m back online.</p>

						<p class="availabilityDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--availabilityIntro">Response times are typically within one business day.</p>
					</div>

					<article class="availabilityDetailsSection__availabilityCard availabilityCard availabilityCard--contactPage">
						<h4 class="availabilityCard__headingH4 headingH4 headingH4--availabilityCard">Availability</h4>
						<ul class="availabilityDetailsSection__hoursList">
							<li class="availabilityDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--availabilityHours"><span>Monday – Friday:</span> 09:00 – 16:00</li>
							<li class="availabilityDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--availabilityHours"><span>Saturday:</span> By Appointment</li>
							<li class="availabilityDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--availabilityHours"><span>Sunday:</span> Closed</li>
						</ul>
					</article>
				</div>
			</section>
			<!-- sectionDivider -->
			<svg class="sectionDivider sectionDivider--designPageServicesSection" viewBox="0 0 1440 1000" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
				<g transform="scale(1, -1) translate(0, -1000)">
					<path fill="#1b90d8" d="M0,600 C420,900 1020,200 1440,600 L1440,0 L0,0 Z" />
					<path fill="#f2f2f2" d="M0,500 C400,1000 1040,100 1440,500 L1440,0 L0,0 Z" />
					<path fill="url(#gradientBlue)" d="M0,400 C360,800 1080,0 1440,400 L1440,0 L0,0 Z" />
				</g>
				<defs>
					<linearGradient id="gradientBlue" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
						<stop offset="0%" stop-color="#1b90d8" stop-opacity="0" />
						<stop offset="30%" stop-color="#1b90d8" stop-opacity="0.25" />
						<stop offset="100%" stop-color="#1b90d8" stop-opacity="1" />
					</linearGradient>
					<linearGradient id="gradientWhite" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
						<stop offset="0%" stop-color="#f2f2f2" stop-opacity="0" />
						<stop offset="100%" stop-color="#f2f2f2" stop-opacity="1" />
					</linearGradient>
					<linearGradient id="gradientDarkBlue" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
						<stop offset="0%" stop-color="#003049" stop-opacity="0" />
						<stop offset="100%" stop-color="#003049" stop-opacity="1" />
					</linearGradient>
				</defs>
			</svg>
			<!-- CONTACT FORM -->
			<section class="contactPage__contactFormSection contactFormSection contactPageSection">
				<div id="sendmessage" class="linkDiv"></div>
				<div class="contactFormSection__sectionHeading sectionHeading">
					<h2 class="contactFormSection__headingH2 sectionHeading__headingH2 headingH2 headingH2--contactForm">Contact Form</h2>
					<hr class="contactFormSection__hr sectionHeading__hr hr hr--contactForm" />
					<p class="contactFormSection__headingH2Tagline sectionHeading__headingH2Tagline headingH2Tagline headingH2Tagline--contactForm">message me right now</p>
				</div>

				<div class="contactPageSection__contactPageSectionContentContainer contactFormSection__contactFormSectionContentContainer">
					<h3 class="contactFormSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--contactForm">Ready to bring your ideas online?</h3>

					<p class="contactFormSection__paragraph contactFormSection__paragraph--intro paragraph paragraph--contactform">
						Whether you need a new website, a redesign of your current site, or expert guidance on improving your online presence, I'm here to help. Use this contact form to tell me about your project, goals,
						and requirements so we can discuss the best solution for your business.
					</p>

					<p class="contactFormSection__paragraph contactFormSection__paragraph--action paragraph paragraph--contactform">
						Complete the form below with as much detail as you'd like, and you'll receive a response within one business.
					</p>

					<p class="contactFormSection__paragraph contactFormSection__paragraph--action paragraph paragraph--contactform">All information submitted hrough this form is handled with care and confidentiality.</p>

					<div class="contactFormSection__formContainer">
						<form class="contactFormSection__form form" action="/contact" method="POST">
							<h3 class="form__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--contactform">Contact Form</h3>

							<div class="form__formRowGroupNamesAndDetails">
								<fieldset class="form__formRow form__formRow--names">
									<legend class="form__headingH4 headingH4 headingH4--contactform">Full Names</legend>

									<!-- <div class="form__inputGroup form__inputGroup--firstname">
										<label for="firstName">First Name</label>
										<input class="form__input paragraph paragraph--input" type="text" id="firstName" name="firstName" required />
									</div> -->

									<div class="form__inputGroup form__inputGroup--firstname">
										<label for="firstName"> First Name <span aria-hidden="true">*</span> </label>

										<input
											class="form__input form__input--firstName paragraph paragraph--input"
											type="text"
											id="firstName"
											name="firstName"
											required
											aria-required="true"
											autocomplete="given-name"
											minlength="2"
											maxlength="50"
											placeholder="" />

										<span class="form__error paragraph paragraph--formError" aria-live="polite"></span>
									</div>

									<div class="form__inputGroup form__inputGroup--lastname">
										<label for="lastName">Last Name</label>
										<input class="form__input form__input--lastName paragraph paragraph--input" type="text" id="lastName" name="lastName" required />
										<span class="form__error paragraph paragraph--formError" aria-live="polite"></span>
									</div>
								</fieldset>

								<fieldset class="form__formRow form__formRow--details">
									<legend class="form__headingH4 headingH4 headingH4--contactform">Contact Details</legend>

									<div class="form__inputGroup form__inputGroup--email">
										<label for="email">Email Address <span aria-hidden="true">*</span> </label>
										<input class="form__input form__input--email paragraph paragraph--input" type="email" id="email" name="email" required />
										<span class="form__error paragraph paragraph--formError" aria-live="polite"></span>
									</div>

									<div class="form__inputGroup form__inputGroup--phonenumber">
										<label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
										<input class="form__input form__input--phonenumber paragraph paragraph--input" type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" />
										<span class="form__error paragraph paragraph--formError" aria-live="polite"></span>
									</div>
								</fieldset>
							</div>

							<fieldset class="form__formRow form__formRow--message">
								<legend class="form__headingH4 headingH4 headingH4--contactform">Message</legend>

								<div class="form__inputGroupContainer">
									<div class="form__inputGroup form__inputGroup--subject">
										<label for="subject">Subject</label>
										<input class="form__input form__input--subject paragraph paragraph--input" type="text" id="subject" name="subject" />
										<span class="form__error paragraph paragraph--formError" aria-live="polite"></span>
									</div>

									<div class="form__inputGroup form__inputGroup--service">
										<label for="service">Service Required</label>

										<select id="service" name="service">
											<option class="form__formSelectOption paragraph paragraph--formSelectOption" value="">Please Select</option>
											<option class="form__formSelectOption paragraph paragraph--formSelectOption" value="web-design">Web Design</option>
											<option class="form__formSelectOption paragraph paragraph--formSelectOption" value="web-development">Web Development</option>
											<option class="form__formSelectOption paragraph paragraph--formSelectOption" value="seo">SEO</option>
											<option class="form__formSelectOption paragraph paragraph--formSelectOption" value="maintenance">Website Maintenance</option>
											<option class="form__formSelectOption paragraph paragraph--formSelectOption" value="other">Other</option>
										</select>
									</div>
								</div>

								<div class="form__inputGroup form__inputGroup--message">
									<label for="message">Message <span aria-hidden="true">*</span> </label>

									<textarea class="form__textarea" id="message" name="message" rows="3" required></textarea>
									<span class="form__error paragraph paragraph--formError" aria-live="polite"></span>
								</div>
							</fieldset>

							<div class="form__submitContainer">
								<button type="submit" class="btn btn--secondary">Send Message</button>
							</div>
						</form>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			<!-- sectionDivider -->
			<svg class="sectionDivider sectionDivider--designPageServicesSection" viewBox="0 0 1440 1000" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
				<g transform="scale(1, -1) translate(0, -1000)">
					<path fill="#1b90d8" d="M0,600 C420,900 1020,200 1440,600 L1440,0 L0,0 Z" />
					<path fill="#f2f2f2" d="M0,500 C400,1000 1040,100 1440,500 L1440,0 L0,0 Z" />
					<path fill="url(#gradientBlue)" d="M0,400 C360,800 1080,0 1440,400 L1440,0 L0,0 Z" />
				</g>
				<defs>
					<linearGradient id="gradientBlue" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
						<stop offset="0%" stop-color="#1b90d8" stop-opacity="0" />
						<stop offset="30%" stop-color="#1b90d8" stop-opacity="0.25" />
						<stop offset="100%" stop-color="#1b90d8" stop-opacity="1" />
					</linearGradient>
					<linearGradient id="gradientWhite" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
						<stop offset="0%" stop-color="#f2f2f2" stop-opacity="0" />
						<stop offset="100%" stop-color="#f2f2f2" stop-opacity="1" />
					</linearGradient>
					<linearGradient id="gradientDarkBlue" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
						<stop offset="0%" stop-color="#003049" stop-opacity="0" />
						<stop offset="100%" stop-color="#003049" stop-opacity="1" />
					</linearGradient>
				</defs>
			</svg>
			<!-- FAQ -->
			<section class="contactPage__faqSection faqSection contactPageSection">
				<div id="faq" class="linkDiv"></div>
				<div class="faqSection__sectionHeading sectionHeading">
					<h2 class="faqSection__headingH2 sectionHeading__headingH2 headingH2 headingH2--faq">FAQ</h2>
					<hr class="faqSection__hr sectionHeading__hr hr hr--faq" />
					<p class="faqSection__headingH2Tagline sectionHeading__headingH2Tagline headingH2Tagline headingH2Tagline--faq">ask me anything</p>
				</div>

				<div class="contactPageSection__contactPageSectionContentContainer">
					<div class="faqSection__faqContainer">
						<article class="faqSection__faqItem">
							<h3 class="faqSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--faq">How quickly do you respond to enquiries?</h3>
							<p class="faqSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--faq">I typically respond to all website design and development enquiries within one business day.</p>
						</article>

						<article class="faqSection__faqItem">
							<h3 class="faqSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--faq">Do you work with clients remotely?</h3>
							<p class="faqSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--faq">
								Yes. I work with clients globally using email, phone, and video calls, making the entire web design process fully remote and efficient.
							</p>
						</article>

						<article class="faqSection__faqItem">
							<h3 class="faqSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--faq">Can I request a quote for my website project?</h3>
							<p class="faqSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--faq">
								Absolutely. Send a detailed message through the contact form, and I’ll provide a tailored quote based on your project requirements.
							</p>
						</article>

						<article class="faqSection__faqItem">
							<h3 class="faqSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--faq">What services do you offer?</h3>
							<p class="faqSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--faq">
								I specialise in custom website design, web development, responsive design, website redesigns, and ongoing maintenance for businesses and individuals.
							</p>
						</article>

						<article class="faqSection__faqItem">
							<h3 class="faqSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--faq">How long does a website take to build?</h3>
							<p class="faqSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--faq">Project timelines vary depending on scope, but most standard business websites take between 2–6 weeks from start to finish.</p>
						</article>

						<article class="faqSection__faqItem">
							<h3 class="faqSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--faq">Do you build mobile-friendly websites?</h3>
							<p class="faqSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--faq">Yes. Every website I build is fully responsive and optimised for mobile, tablet, and desktop devices.</p>
						</article>

						<article class="faqSection__faqItem">
							<h3 class="faqSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--faq">Will my website be SEO-friendly?</h3>
							<p class="faqSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--faq">
								Yes. All websites are built with SEO best practices in mind, including clean code, fast loading speeds, and proper on-page structure.
							</p>
						</article>

						<article class="faqSection__faqItem">
							<h3 class="faqSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--faq">Do you offer website maintenance after launch?</h3>
							<p class="faqSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--faq">Yes. I offer optional maintenance and support packages to keep your website secure, updated, and running smoothly.</p>
						</article>

						<article class="faqSection__faqItem">
							<h3 class="faqSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--faq">Can you redesign my existing website?</h3>
							<p class="faqSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--faq">
								Yes. I can redesign outdated websites to improve usability, performance, and modern visual appeal while keeping your brand identity intact.
							</p>
						</article>

						<article class="faqSection__faqItem">
							<h3 class="faqSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--faq">What do you need to get started on a project?</h3>
							<p class="faqSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--faq">
								To get started, I typically need a brief overview of your goals, any existing branding or content, and examples of websites you like.
							</p>
						</article>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
